00:26:39.731 --> 00:26:41.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The priority order is absolute</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in a disaster.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:26:45.904 --> 00:26:48.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's marked green.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Don't let your emotions interfere!</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:26:48.506 --> 00:26:51.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-But!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Once she drinks this, she'll be fine.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:26:51.610 --> 00:26:54.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Calm down.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>She's not crying from an injury.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:26:54.879 --> 00:26:56.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's just a stomachache.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:26:57.182 --> 00:26:59.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are from the Igakukan?</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:26:59.351 --> 00:27:02.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it's something Chinese medicine</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can handle, I'll help as well!</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:27:05.991 --> 00:27:07.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Move her here!</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:27:08.126 --> 00:27:09.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Next patient, please!</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:27:11.997 --> 00:27:13.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This may feel a little cold.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:27:20.605 --> 00:27:22.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The treatment area is over here!</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:27:23.775 --> 00:27:25.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here we go!</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:27:26.645 --> 00:27:29.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Next, over here!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Right!</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:27:32.484 --> 00:27:35.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Senkichi, break the downwind!</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:27:38.189 --> 00:27:40.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, Senkichi!</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:27:44.729 --> 00:27:45.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Senkichi!</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:27:50.635 --> 00:27:52.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Senkichi!</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:28:02.213 --> 00:28:05.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are fewer patients now.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Saki, hang in there a little longer.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:28:06.217 --> 00:28:09.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Make way! It's an emergency!</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:28:10.555 --> 00:28:13.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Bring him over here.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Hurry up!</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:28:15.060 --> 00:28:16.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. Senkichi!</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:28:16.161 --> 00:28:18.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was struggling inside the fire.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:28:20.565 --> 00:28:23.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it's a thermal airway injury.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Get the resuscitator!</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:28:23.401 --> 00:28:24.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Right.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:28:37.082 --> 00:28:39.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's too stiff. The air isn't going in.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:28:39.350 --> 00:28:42.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you that kind of thing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wouldn't work!</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:28:44.956 --> 00:28:47.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When it gets this bad,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there's nothing you can do.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:28:48.827 --> 00:28:51.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've seen this happen many times.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:28:52.363 --> 00:28:55.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey! Let's carry Senkichi to the monk.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:28:55.500 --> 00:28:56.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir!</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:28:57.335 --> 00:28:58.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't touch my patient!</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:28:59.704 --> 00:29:02.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's cut his throat. Saki, get ready.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:29:02.107 --> 00:29:03.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did you say?</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:29:03.174 --> 00:29:06.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. Senkichi inhaled hot smoke and air,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>burning the inside of his throat.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:29:06.978 --> 00:29:09.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>His throat is swollen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and he can't breathe.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:29:10.515 --> 00:29:13.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we cut the throat and insert a tube,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he'll be able to breathe.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:29:14.052 --> 00:29:16.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you cut his throat, he'll die for sure!</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:29:16.488 --> 00:29:17.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we don't cut it, he'll die.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:29:17.856 --> 00:29:20.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-This is ridiculous. Let's go!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes, sir!</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:29:21.259 --> 00:29:22.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stop!</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:29:25.764 --> 00:29:27.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why aren't you trying to save lives?!</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:29:27.999 --> 00:29:30.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we operate, we can save Mr. Senkichi!</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:29:31.803 --> 00:29:34.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dying in a fire</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is the wish of a firefighter.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:29:34.806 --> 00:29:38.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But if he dies with his throat cut,</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:29:38.610 --> 00:29:40.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Senkichi won't be able to rest in peace.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:29:41.412 --> 00:29:43.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's the spirit of a firefighter.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:29:45.483 --> 00:29:47.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are countless lives</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that we cannot save.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:29:48.820 --> 00:29:52.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But if I ignore the lives I can save,</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:29:52.991 --> 00:29:55.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>then I won't rest in peace, even in death!</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:29:56.427 --> 00:29:57.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's the spirit of a doctor!</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:30:02.333 --> 00:30:04.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>His lips are turning blue.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:30:07.872 --> 00:30:09.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's showing signs of cyanosis.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:30:09.474 --> 00:30:12.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll call any available doctor!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Please do.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:30:18.516 --> 00:30:20.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Senkichi is my right-hand man.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:30:21.419 --> 00:30:24.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If he dies, I'll be taking your right arm</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as payment. Let's go!</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:30:25.156 --> 00:30:26.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir!</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:30:41.339 --> 00:30:43.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aren't you going to use anesthesia?</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:30:43.508 --> 00:30:45.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He needs air, there's no time for that!</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:30:45.643 --> 00:30:47.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Hold him down firmly.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:30:53.785 --> 00:30:54.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:30:54.886 --> 00:30:57.088 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm injecting air</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>directly with this syringe.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:30:57.155 --> 00:30:58.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hold him steady!</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:31:06.598 --> 00:31:07.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Airway secured.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:31:18.243 --> 00:31:20.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's go. Make sure to hold him steady.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:31:20.311 --> 00:31:21.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Right.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:31:33.691 --> 00:31:35.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The wind has changed.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:31:35.126 --> 00:31:38.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief! The treatment area</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is on the downwind side.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:31:38.496 --> 00:31:39.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shall we send a message?</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:31:40.531 --> 00:31:42.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't let the fire spread</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even if it kills you!</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:31:43.268 --> 00:31:45.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's the spirit of Edo's firefighters!</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:31:46.070 --> 00:31:47.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes!</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:31:53.478 --> 00:31:56.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Move quickly! Hurry!</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:32:09.594 --> 00:32:12.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What kind of treatment is this?</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:32:15.366 --> 00:32:17.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The fire is closing in on us!</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:32:18.503 --> 00:32:20.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've evacuated the mobile patients.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:32:20.305 --> 00:32:22.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctors, please relocate the surgery site!</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:32:23.908 --> 00:32:25.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Close the door.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:32:26.177 --> 00:32:27.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're in the middle of surgery.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:32:29.280 --> 00:32:31.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can't move the patient now.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:32:32.383 --> 00:32:33.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you want to leave, go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:32:35.386 --> 00:32:37.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Do you plan on dying?!</i></c.bg_transparent>

411
00:32:54.005 --> 00:32:57.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When it collapses,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cover it with mats soaked in water.</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:32:58.042 --> 00:33:00.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Protect your station with your life!</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:33:05.817 --> 00:33:07.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The tracheotomy is complete.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:33:07.185 --> 00:33:08.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Tracheal suction.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:33:40.852 --> 00:33:44.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor, there's not that much soot</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in his phlegm…</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:33:44.222 --> 00:33:46.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The burn hasn't spread</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to his lungs or lower trachea.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:33:47.158 --> 00:33:49.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Alright. Cannula!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:33:56.367 --> 00:33:57.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And next?</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:33:58.536 --> 00:34:00.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we remove the inner tube</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and he starts breathing,</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:34:00.972 --> 00:34:02.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. Senkichi will live.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:34:18.289 --> 00:34:20.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's do this all at once!</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:34:20.124 --> 00:34:22.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here we go!</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:34:23.027 --> 00:34:24.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here I go.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:34:38.743 --> 00:34:40.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's down!</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:34:49.954 --> 00:34:51.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alright… he's breathing!</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:34:51.889 --> 00:34:52.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes!</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:35:19.183 --> 00:35:20.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The surgery is complete.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:35:20.551 --> 00:35:21.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shall we go outside?</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:35:22.520 --> 00:35:23.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Please.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:35:25.957 --> 00:35:26.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor!</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:35:32.997 --> 00:35:33.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is…</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:35:38.102 --> 00:35:41.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The buildings… are all gone.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:35:56.521 --> 00:35:57.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The fire's out.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:35:58.823 --> 00:36:00.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are things over there?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:36:03.728 --> 00:36:04.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was saved.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:36:16.541 --> 00:36:18.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see you didn't run away.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:36:20.611 --> 00:36:23.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The spirit of a doctor is truly something.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:36:26.184 --> 00:36:28.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a firefighter through and through,</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:36:30.388 --> 00:36:32.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but you're a doctor through and through.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:36:34.592 --> 00:36:36.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. It's nothing as impressive as that.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:36:38.696 --> 00:36:40.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To be honest, I wasn't sure what to do…</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:36:43.935 --> 00:36:44.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:36:46.204 --> 00:36:47.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I decided to believe</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:36:49.807 --> 00:36:51.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in the spirit of Edo's firefighters.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:36:54.612 --> 00:36:55.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's why I could do it.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:36:57.682 --> 00:36:58.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you very much.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:37:02.787 --> 00:37:03.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief Tatsugoro.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:37:05.756 --> 00:37:07.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Damn it, you rascal!</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:37:37.321 --> 00:37:38.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No matter how great you are,</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:37:38.956 --> 00:37:41.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't forgive you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for abandoning me, Doctor!</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:37:44.495 --> 00:37:45.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where is the Doctor?</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:37:48.299 --> 00:37:50.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He went to the fire.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-A fire?</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:37:52.169 --> 00:37:53.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>While I was sleeping?</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:37:54.272 --> 00:37:56.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Things were going so well,</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:37:58.175 --> 00:37:59.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I lost to the fire.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:37:59.910 --> 00:38:01.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Going well…?</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:38:10.721 --> 00:38:14.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But why did you seduce him?</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:38:15.359 --> 00:38:17.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't really seem like your style.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:38:18.262 --> 00:38:20.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Between the Doctor and Ms. Saki,</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:38:21.565 --> 00:38:22.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>there's medicine.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:38:24.902 --> 00:38:29.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I, too, wanted something to bind us.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:38:30.074 --> 00:38:35.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then, I thought</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I could leave this place without regret.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:38:36.747 --> 00:38:37.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Leave?</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:38:41.252 --> 00:38:42.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I…</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:38:44.121 --> 00:38:45.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>am being bought out.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:38:48.025 --> 00:38:50.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It may sound nice, but…</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:38:51.395 --> 00:38:56.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will just become a caged bird</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>inside a mansion this time.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:38:57.935 --> 00:38:59.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And then,</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:39:00.237 --> 00:39:03.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't be able to meet the doctor</c.bg_transparent>
