470
00:39:04.508 --> 00:39:05.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just once I wished to…</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:39:08.913 --> 00:39:12.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's truly painful, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:39:13.150 --> 00:39:14.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To be cast aside like that.</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:39:17.588 --> 00:39:19.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I made a living by selling love,</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:39:21.025 --> 00:39:25.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I didn't understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>such feelings at all.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:39:29.100 --> 00:39:33.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I truly learned something good</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from Dr. Minakata.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:39:37.708 --> 00:39:39.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you want to cry, just go ahead and cry!</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:39:39.677 --> 00:39:42.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The tears of a courtesan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are flowers of deceit.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:39:44.382 --> 00:39:47.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To shed honest tears for love</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:39:49.653 --> 00:39:51.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>would tarnish the name of a courtesan.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:39:59.897 --> 00:40:02.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This way, I won't see your face.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:40:15.446 --> 00:40:16.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:40:19.283 --> 00:40:20.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to become like snow.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:40:24.955 --> 00:40:26.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I become snow,</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:40:29.326 --> 00:40:31.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>anytime and anywhere…</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:40:34.131 --> 00:40:35.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could fall</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:40:37.701 --> 00:40:40.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>onto the Doctor's shoulders.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:40:55.286 --> 00:40:56.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>After the commotion of the fire,</i></c.bg_transparent>

488
00:40:57.588 --> 00:40:59.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I thought for a moment,</i></c.bg_transparent>

489
00:41:00.491 --> 00:41:03.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>that if this fire hadn't happened</i></c.bg_transparent>

490
00:41:03.694 --> 00:41:05.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>and I had stayed with her,</i></c.bg_transparent>

491
00:41:10.568 --> 00:41:15.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>would Miki have regained her color?</i></c.bg_transparent>

492
00:41:34.058 --> 00:41:36.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A… lump?</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:41:56.013 --> 00:41:57.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Next, please.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:42:00.117 --> 00:42:00.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How is this?</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:42:01.018 --> 00:42:02.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Will you build a hospital?</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:42:02.419 --> 00:42:05.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You always need a place like this</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when there's a fire, right?</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:42:07.691 --> 00:42:10.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Well… Yes.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Then it's settled.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:42:11.395 --> 00:42:13.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fires are waiting for us.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:42:14.798 --> 00:42:16.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're a firefighter to the bone.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:42:19.603 --> 00:42:24.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A long time ago, during a fire,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I demolished a house.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:42:25.609 --> 00:42:28.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The wind was so strong</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that we had no choice.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:42:29.747 --> 00:42:34.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But a woman</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was once in love with was in there.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:42:35.686 --> 00:42:38.088 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She was trapped in there and died.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:42:40.291 --> 00:42:42.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even though I saved countless strangers,</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:42:43.460 --> 00:42:45.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I ended up killing the woman I loved.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:42:51.168 --> 00:42:56.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to keep fighting fires until I die.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:43:02.279 --> 00:43:05.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mother, what do you wish to discuss?</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:43:05.416 --> 00:43:09.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A marriage proposal has arrived for you.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:43:12.590 --> 00:43:13.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For me?</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:43:28.405 --> 00:43:31.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What could be affecting Miki's existence?</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:43:40.618 --> 00:43:41.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor…</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:43:46.223 --> 00:43:50.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is there something wrong</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the photograph?</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:43:52.162 --> 00:43:55.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been concerned about it lately.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:43:57.601 --> 00:43:58.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:44:09.847 --> 00:44:12.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor, actually I…</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:44:13.450 --> 00:44:19.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Father, I have one request.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:44:20.224 --> 00:44:24.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Before the marriage arrangement,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there will be a physical examination.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:44:25.796 --> 00:44:32.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would like to ask</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Minakata to perform it.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:44:34.338 --> 00:44:35.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did something happen to you?</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:44:39.076 --> 00:44:40.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually…</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:44:41.745 --> 00:44:42.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes?</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:44:56.326 --> 00:45:00.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>What is Sakamoto</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>planning to do with penicillin?</i></c.bg_transparent>

523
00:45:00.698 --> 00:45:02.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems he's trying to sell it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Joi-faction</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:45:02.933 --> 00:45:04.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>since it's effective against syphilis.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:45:04.635 --> 00:45:06.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sell it? What for?</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:45:06.203 --> 00:45:08.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When their life depends on it…</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:45:09.506 --> 00:45:12.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>some may abandon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their devotion to expel foreigners.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:45:12.409 --> 00:45:13.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. Kusaka!</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:45:13.444 --> 00:45:18.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps that is the real aim.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:45:18.716 --> 00:45:22.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I also received a secret letter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from someone wanting to talk to me.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:45:23.921 --> 00:45:27.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We must kill Sakamoto, then.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:45:28.692 --> 00:45:31.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong, Doctor?</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:45:32.896 --> 00:45:34.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The pain that I had forgotten</i></c.bg_transparent>

534
00:45:35.299 --> 00:45:37.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>brings back buried memories.</i></c.bg_transparent>

535
00:45:40.070 --> 00:45:42.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm going back, to that world.</i></c.bg_transparent>

536
00:45:43.440 --> 00:45:45.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I see… That is…</i></c.bg_transparent>

537
00:45:49.980 --> 00:45:50.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor!</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:46:02.025 --> 00:46:05.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Thank you for everything until now,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dr. Minakata.</i></c.bg_transparent>

539
00:46:05.129 --> 00:46:07.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Do you know our fate, Doctor?</i></c.bg_transparent>

540
00:46:07.231 --> 00:46:09.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I was certain it was cancer.</i></c.bg_transparent>

541
00:46:09.399 --> 00:46:12.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Medicine sometimes reveals even the heart.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:46:12.536 --> 00:46:13.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's go!</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:46:13.537 --> 00:46:16.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ryoma Sakamoto can't die here.</i></c.bg_transparent>

544
00:46:16.807 --> 00:46:19.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have a lump in my chest.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:46:20.511 --> 00:46:22.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If so, it's a lethal illness!</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:46:22.513 --> 00:46:25.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing, Doctor? Go back!</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:46:25.082 --> 00:46:27.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Were you going to let Ms. Nokaze die?</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:46:27.618 --> 00:46:30.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Lives will be needlessly lost.</i></c.bg_transparent>

549
00:46:30.287 --> 00:46:32.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I like you very much, Ms. Saki.</i></c.bg_transparent>

550
00:46:32.689 --> 00:46:34.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I cannot endure this.</i></c.bg_transparent>

551
00:46:34.358 --> 00:46:36.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Saki, please be happy.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:46:37.161 --> 00:46:39.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Everything will end soon.</i></c.bg_transparent>

